Whitehaven



	Whitehaven apron-front kitchen sink features a streamlined and versatile farmhouse style to complement any decor. Perfect for remodeling projects, it has a shortened apron that allows for installation on most new or existing 36-inch standard cabinetry. The Self-Trimming design requires only a simple rough cut, overlapping the cabinet face for beautiful results and easy installation. A large single basin accommodates large pots and pans, while the sloped bottom helps with draining and cleanup. Crafted from enameled cast iron, this sink resists chipping, cracking, or burning for years of beauty and reliable performance.
	





Product Features:


Covered under Kohler's limited lifetime warranty
Single basin design provides maximum workspace
The Whitehaven apron-front sink features a streamlined and versatile farmhouse style
A large basin accommodates large pots and pans, while the sloped bottom helps with draining and clean-up
Constructed of enameled cast iron, which combines strength, durability, and insulation benefits
Undermount installation with apron front gives an integrated, graceful look to the sink
Offset drain location increases workspace area in the sink as well as storage space underneath
All hardware needed for installation included


Product Technologies / Benefits:


Enameled Cast-Iron:  Kohler Enameled Cast-Iron combines the strength, durability, and insulation benefits of cast-iron with the scratch, chip, and burn resistance of a baked, powder coat finish and comes with an exceptional Lifetime Limited Warranty. When these materials are combined it gives the sink or tub the strength to last a lifetime of use. Kohler Enameled Cast-Iron is also available in a wide variety of specialty colors allowing you to truly customize your home.

Apron Front: Kohler apron front sinks have a stylish panel in front and are available in both drop-in (also called tile-in) and undermount configurations. Sometimes called a "farmhouse sink", this beautiful style evokes the charm of a traditional kitchen and can be installed with only minor modifications to existing kitchen cabinetry and countertops.
Self-Trimming: A style of apron front sink design in which the apron overlaps a portion of the existing kitchen cabinetry. This allows the installation of an apron front sink with only minor countertop modification.


Product Specifications:


Height: 9-5/8" (measured from bottom of sink to top of rim)
Overall Width: 21-9/16" (measured from back outer rim to front outer rim)
Overall Length: 35-1/2" (measured from left outer rim to right outer rim)
Basin Width: 18-1/16" (measured from back inner rim to front inner rim)
Basin Length: 30-3/4" (measured from left inner rim to right inner rim)
Basin Depth: 9" (measured from center of basin to rim)
Installation Type: Undermount / Farmhouse
Drain Outlet Connection: 3-5/8"
Minimum Base Cabinet Width: 36"







About Kohler:


 Gracious living is characterized by qualities of charm, good taste, generosity of spirit, and the enhancement of nature. It is Kohler's mission that you improve your sense of gracious living with every experience you have with a Kohler product or service. Kohler lives on the leading edge of design and technology, while maintaining a constant level of quality, regardless of price. It sets the standard of excellence in its field, and yet is constantly striving to improve. From sustainable products in the kitchen and bath to power systems that protect data centers and urban landscapes all over the world - this is what the Kohler company is all about.
