Item #: LHT-47-SG
Price: $9,662.00
Sale Price: $7,440.00


		Our ULTRA TOUCH Series sliding glass door laboratory refrigerators are ideal for a variety of research applications with the need to safely store temperature critical samples. Constructed with sample security in mind, these general-purpose upright refrigerators feature audible & visual high/ low temperature alarms and remote alarm contacts for complete temperature control and awareness. The LHT-47-SG comes standard with two glass doors, touchscreen display, microprocessor controller, LED interior lights, built-in data logger and USB port for data transfer and software updates.

		 

Specifications:


			Cu. Ft.: 47

			Door(s): Two sliding glass doors, self-closing (energy efficient, double pane vacuum insulated)

			Temperature Range: 1°C to 10°C

			Exterior Dimensions: 54 1/8"W x 30 3/4"D x 82 5/8” H with casters; 78 5/8” H without casters

			Interior Dimensions: 50 1/4"W x 22 1/2"D x 56 1/2” H

			Alarm: Audible and visual high/low temperature alarms

			Shelves: 8 adjustable shelves (adjustable in ½" increments)

			Keyed Door Lock

			Electrical Requirements:  115V, 60Hz ; 8.5 amps ; 1/2 HP

			UL/C-UL listed

			Shipping Weight: 505 lbs.


Features:


			Cycle defrost

			Microprocessor temperature controller

			Touch Screen Digital Temperature Display and Alarm Module

			Password-protected control panel

			Sample simulated digital temperature display; .1° Resolution

			Adjustable temperature display in Celsius or Fahrenheit

			Active temperature scale bar display

			Resettable 1-point min/max history

			Digital 24-hour temperature chart

			Temperature & alarm event data logging

			USB port for data transfer and software updates

			Real-time operational display clock

			4-20mA output

			Electronic troubleshooting guide

			Electronic QR Code to access Owner’s Manual & technical support contact Information

			Adjustable alarm volume

			Audible and visual high/low temperature alarms

			Sensor error alarm

			Power failure alarm

			Door ajar alarm

			Low battery alarm

			Operation indicator

			Alarm testing capabilities

			Alarm mute with ring back

			Remote alarm contacts

			Magnetic door gasket for positive seal

			Recessed door handle

			Casters

			LED interior lights are safety shielded and switch controlled

			Probe access port (3/8")

			HFC-free refrigerant (R290a), foam insulation and packaging

			Forced draft air circulation

			Warranty: 3 years parts and labor, plus an addtional 2 years compressor parts only



